# Robinhood MCP — live portfolio (read-only)

For **live** Robinhood holdings in StockPick (daily trader workflow):

1. **Sync script:** `./scripts/sync-robinhood-mcp.sh` or `POST /api/brokerage/sync/robinhood-mcp`
2. **First-time auth:** `./scripts/robinhood-mcp-login.sh` (tokens → `storage/robinhood_mcp/`)
3. **Docs:** [docs/ROBINHOOD_MCP.md](../../docs/ROBINHOOD_MCP.md)

Read-only MCP tools only: `get_accounts`, `get_portfolio`, `get_equity_positions`. Do **not** call trade tools unless the user explicitly requests agentic trading.

Cursor IDE MCP (`robinhood-trading` in `.cursor/mcp.json`) is separate — use StockPick sync to persist into the app database.
